<paragraph blockId="1.[136,1452,302,436]" pageId="1" pageNumber="51">
<bibRefCitation author="Cavanilles, A. J." box="[136,338,302,328]" pageId="1" pageNumber="51" refId="ref1533" refString="Cavanilles, A. J. (1793) Icones et Descriptiones Plantarum 2. Typographia Regia, Madrid, 32 pp." type="book" year="1793">Cavanilles (1793)</bibRefCitation>
described this species from the Sagunto area of 
<collectingCountry box="[899,963,302,328]" name="Spain" pageId="1" pageNumber="51">Spain</collectingCountry>
(“Habitat in Saguntinae arcis vetustissimo muro”). The iconography is original material for the name and perfectly depicts all of the morphological details of this species. 
<collectionCode box="[231,240,374,400]" country="Romania" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14415" name="&amp;quot;Alexandru Ioan Cuza&amp;quot; University" pageId="1" pageNumber="51" type="Herbarium">I</collectionCode>
was not able to trace further original materials. For this reason the iconography is selected as the 
<typeStatus box="[1342,1448,374,400]" pageId="1" pageNumber="51">lectotype</typeStatus>
. The 
<typeStatus box="[187,290,410,436]" pageId="1" pageNumber="51">lectotype</typeStatus>
confirms the current application of the name (e.g. 
<bibRefCitation author="Chater, A. O. &amp; Cartier, D." box="[858,1112,410,436]" pageId="1" pageNumber="51" pagination="38 - 44" refId="ref1556" refString="Chater, A. O. &amp; Cartier, D. (1976) Plantago L. In: Tutin, T. G., Burges, N. A., Chater, A. O., Heywood, V. H., Moore, D. M., Valentine, D. H., Walters, S. M. &amp; Webb, D. A. (Eds.) Flora Europaea 4. Cambridge University Press, Cambridge, pp. 38 - 44." type="book chapter" year="1976">
Chater &amp; 
<collectingCountry box="[968,1046,410,436]" name="Ashmore and Cartier Islands" pageId="1" pageNumber="51">Cartier</collectingCountry>
1976
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Pignatti, S." box="[1123,1277,410,436]" pageId="1" pageNumber="51" refId="ref2232" refString="Pignatti, S. (1982) Flora d'Italia 2. Edagricole, Bologna, 732 pp." type="book" year="1982">Pignatti 1982</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
